comment: I won‚Äôt be watching POTC6 for one reason and it‚Äôs not just because Depp‚Äôs not in it. It‚Äôs due to the story. While it is supposed to be Will‚Äôs and Elizabeth‚Äôs story, Jack Sparrow was just supposed to be a side character. But instead Disney had pushed Jack so much that he eventually became the main character, which I would say is why Disney is loosing profits cause they went just by what fans wanted instead of being truthful to the story. Now, Jack in my opinion is watered down due to a story that wasn‚Äôt his being placed upon him and to just take (Depp‚Äôs) Jack away is like a slap to the fans. If they‚Äôre going to tell a story about just Jack Sparrow, why not do a prequel on one of his many stories in the movies like how he lost the pearl after being betrayed by Barbossa or how he saved all those slaves and his soul was debted to Davy Jones? Distance him from POTC and do something like ‚ÄúSparrow‚Äù. Give the fans something they want while finally giving a end to a previous story that should‚Äôve ended a long time ago. And yes, I am suggesting that something along the lines of Solo should happen as both characters are similar in that they‚Äôre interesting but theyrenot the main character of their story. Their story is in the past, before the movies. But no, Disney is still just after quantity over quality. You already forced a story on a side character and took attention away from the people who were supposed to be there, but now you‚Äôre forcing fans to watch a movie their favorite character isn‚Äôt in while still demonizing his actor for something he couldn‚Äôt control? Shameful.
